OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings survivor
OL,4,Crecalls 'nightmares for 20 years'
OL,6,FA man who survived the Birmingham pub
OL,7,Fbombings has shared his experience for
OL,8,Fthe first time in 50 years, and
OL,9,Freveals he spent the next 20 years
OL,10,Fafter the bombings waking up in the
OL,11,Fmiddle of the night in a cold sweat.
OL,13,FIRA bombs exploded at the The Tavern
OL,14,Fin the Town and The Mulberry Bush pubs
OL,15,Fin 1974, killing 21 people and
OL,16,Finjuring 182 others.
OL,18,FMick O'Brien was in The Tavern in the
OL,19,FTown at the time, but managed to
OL,20,Fsurvive.
