OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings survivor
OL,4,Crecalls 'nightmares for 20 years'
OL,6,FRecalling the moments before the
OL,7,Fexplosion to ITV News Central
OL,8,FCorrespondent Mark Gough, Mr O'Brien
OL,9,Fsaid: "I was going up to get a pint
OL,10,Ffrom the bartender.
OL,12,F"There was a blast then I couldn't
OL,13,Fhear anything because my eardrum was
OL,14,Fburst.
OL,16,F"I was on the floor, people were
OL,17,Fstaggering around, groaning, moaning
OL,18,Fand screaming, and I could smell dust.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
