OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings survivor
OL,4,Crecalls 'nightmares for 20 years'
OL,6,F"That was the thing I remember most:
OL,7,Fdust. It was in my mouth, it was
OL,8,Feverywhere."
OL,10,F"I staggered up what remained of the
OL,11,Fstairs, the cab drivers and passers by
OL,12,Fwere picking people up and taking
OL,13,Feveryone to the hospital.
OL,15,F"I had flecks of glass in my scalp
OL,16,Fwhich were washing out for weeks
OL,17,Fafterwards, but all in all I'm lucky I
OL,18,Fgot out."
