OL,3,CBirmingham pub bombings survivor
OL,4,Crecalls 'nightmares for 20 years'
OL,6,F"It affected me for probably 20 years
OL,7,Fafterwards with nightmares and waking
OL,8,Fup in the middle of the night in a
OL,9,Fcold sweat.
OL,11,F"In the last 25 or 30 years it's faded
OL,12,Foff a little. I still have occasional
OL,13,Fmemories of it but I try to force them
OL,14,Fout.
OL,16,F"It's helpful, telling somebody else
OL,17,Fabout it."
